Title: Macros in dashlet titles
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1612365600
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0b6

When setting custom dashlet titles using the configuration
option "Custom title", you can now use macros such as
<tt>$HOST_NAME$</tt>. The available macros depend on the
dashlet type and are listed in the corresponding help text.
